N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4111.30 - Declaration by person suspended

State Regulations

Declaration shall not be filed for any horse owned or
controlled wholly or in part by a person who does not hold a license issued by
the commission, or whose license has been fully suspended or
revoked. Notes
